{
    "data": [
        {
            "title": "梵蒂岡：教宗方濟各病情穩定 未再發生呼吸危機",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"梵蒂岡稱教宗方濟各病情穩定。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b70aa6ec2a7880563c12ffff78cbe27f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250302/_2025030208072580410.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">梵蒂岡稱教宗方濟各病情穩定。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>梵蒂岡週六表示，教宗方濟各因雙肺炎住院兩週多，目前病情穩定，未出現進一步的呼吸危機。\n\n</p>\n<p>路透社報道，88歲的教宗方濟各週五出現一次支氣管痙攣危機，導致吸入性嘔吐，以及呼吸系統突然惡化，並因此接受支氣管抽吸和非侵入性呼吸器治療。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4112625/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"梵蒂岡稱教宗方濟各未出現進一步的呼吸危機。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/79cd8266ad866343c78c682273f666be/2025-03/2025-02-14T102222Z_1358351038_RC2WSCAEV43P_RTRMADP_3_POPE-HEALTH.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        梵蒂岡稱教宗方濟各未出現進一步的呼吸危機。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4112627/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"信眾為教宗祈禱。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c4a8127457867dd761094e0661df5800/2025-03/2025-03-01T203016Z_1904565800_RC2K4DAYIHTD_RTRMADP_3_POPE-FRANCIS-HEALTH.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        信眾為教宗祈禱。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4112628/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"信眾為教宗祈禱。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2ca8c870b52a0e2a11208b2ffb555cb6/2025-03/2025-03-01T203852Z_1065456006_RC2K4DAIJSMG_RTRMADP_3_POPE-FRANCIS-HEALTH.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        信眾為教宗祈禱。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4112630/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"教宗方濟各仍在醫院留醫。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/40c93e53856b824062b61975722edbb0/2025-03/2025-03-01T165827Z_1374469211_RC2G4DAIA7YU_RTRMADP_3_POPE-FRANCIS-HEALTH.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        教宗方濟各仍在醫院留醫。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4112631/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"教宗方濟各仍在醫院留醫。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a6443a55b38f08f4bc745dc630eac901/2025-03/2025-03-01T173531Z_873865892_RC2H4DA2LWRR_RTRMADP_3_POPE-FRANCIS-HEALTH.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        教宗方濟各仍在醫院留醫。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>梵蒂岡在周六更新教宗病情時表示，教宗沒有發燒，也沒有出現白血球計數升高的跡象，的血流和循環保持穩定。梵蒂岡表示：「教宗的臨床狀況保持穩定」。聲明稱，對病情的預期仍不確定，意味著教宗尚未脫離危險。\n\n</p>\n<p>天空新聞引述一名消息人士稱，教宗的呼吸現在略有改善，但醫生仍保持謹慎，仍然需要更多時間來確定他在昨天的事件後病情是否惡化。消息人士說，教宗病情目前沒有進一步感染的跡象，今天他祈禱 20 分鐘，並喝了一些咖啡。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2055756/即時-國際-梵蒂岡-教宗方濟各病情穩定-未再發生呼吸危機",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-02 08:16:16",
            "source": "stheadline",
