            "title": "西甲｜貝迪斯靠倒戈的艾斯高包辦入球助攻 爆冷2:1擊敗皇家馬德里",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"貝迪斯靠倒戈的艾斯高包辦入球助攻，爆冷2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/af9ed11a77c02fd74bc705b5e933bdc8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250302/_2025030208015066505.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">貝迪斯靠倒戈的艾斯高包辦入球助攻，爆冷2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>貝迪斯於周六的西甲主場對皇家馬德里，憑藉倒戈的艾斯高包辦1個入球和1次助攻，爆冷以2:1擊敗皇馬，阻止對手進佔西甲榜首。伊斯高賽後不敢邀功，指今仗是團隊合力取得的成果。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯中場艾斯高(左)為貝迪斯射入12碼。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2445ccfefbfcc7ac17f60cfabaf1fccf/2025-03/Spain_Soccer_La_Liga_58527--e7c21.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯中場艾斯高(左)為貝迪斯射入12碼。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯中場艾斯高(右)貢獻1球1助攻。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b257f22d0cbddf328bea177cf8b8f12a/2025-03/Spain_Soccer_La_Liga_89737--c4abd.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯中場艾斯高(右)貢獻1球1助攻。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯中場艾斯高(左)貢獻1球1助攻。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7807c108669060549cc01a98fa7fe574/2025-03/2025-03-01T185324Z_2038639944_UP1EL311GGYUW_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-BET-RMA-REPORT_1_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯中場艾斯高(左)貢獻1球1助攻。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/01c2e9671ddb06a0c019d1e4537b1689/2025-03/2025-03-01T184954Z_1321637962_UP1EL311GB5UK_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-BET-RMA-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯(綠白衫)2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3e8ae88f70a9b042ed7e7a8f42a04f66/2025-03/2025-03-01T184053Z_1894046718_UP1EL311FW2TW_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-BET-RMA-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯(綠白衫)2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯(綠白衫)2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/869a502797755e8efce584f0e4d70ae5/2025-03/2025-03-01T184800Z_1257492374_UP1EL311G7ZUG_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-BET-RMA-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯(綠白衫)2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯(綠白衫)2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d18592ab163b3297cddb96d2d72a81bc/2025-03/2025-03-01T192014Z_1793679907_RC2I4DA03787_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-BET-RMA-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯(綠白衫)2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"皇馬前鋒雲尼斯奧斯祖利亞(上)引球衝關。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a24fe98186fdce4a5ad47d0126b74327/2025-03/2025-03-01T192047Z_33138272_UP1EL311HQLXB_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-BET-RMA-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        皇馬前鋒雲尼斯奧斯祖利亞(上)引球衝關。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯(綠白衫)2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6a2c3d1697a7215473793c45eeb1f704/2025-03/2025-03-01T192445Z_729373314_UP1EL311HX7XW_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-BET-RMA-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯(綠白衫)2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雲尼斯奧斯(中)與貝迪斯球員爭執。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3b95b159f45057206ad6239cfb4803cd/2025-03/2025-03-01T193353Z_1560535906_UP1EL311ICFYK_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-BET-RMA-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲尼斯奧斯(中)與貝迪斯球員爭執。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯(綠白衫)2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8d366f57cac6ce3dbe6c6803aeb4e5f3/2025-03/2025-03-01T193504Z_585947415_UP1EL311IEDYN_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-BET-RMA-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯(綠白衫)2:1擊敗皇家馬德里。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>巴謙戴亞斯為皇馬先開紀錄</h2>\n<p>作客的皇馬甫開賽即反客為主，並於10分鐘由前鋒基利安麥巴比策動攻勢，於中路直線妙傳給左邊的費蘭特文迪，後者第一時間將球傳中，中場巴謙戴亞斯門前輕鬆將球送入網，為皇馬先開紀錄。3分鐘後，皇馬翼鋒洛迪高高斯接應左路底線傳中，禁區右邊窄位頭槌頂高。23分鐘，輪到皇馬前鋒雲尼斯奧斯祖利亞於左邊窄位起腳，皮球於楣頂高出。\n\n</p><h2>半場打成1:1</h2>\n<p>貝迪斯捱過皇馬一輪強攻後，於34分鐘由倒戈的艾斯高左路角球傳中，中場莊尼卡度素門前頭槌破網為主隊扳平。上半場補時階段貝迪斯有反超前機會，艾斯高再次主踢左路角球，同樣由莊尼卡度素前柱接應頭槌攻門，但今次被皇馬門將泰拔高圖爾斯將球撲出；半場雙方打成1:1。\n\n</p><h2>艾斯高1入球1助攻</h2>\n<p>換邊後，貝迪斯於53分鐘有前鋒謝斯洛迪古斯禁區內被皇馬中堅魯迪格從後踢跌獲12碼，艾斯高操刀極刑中鵠，個人包辦入球助攻各一，為主隊反勝2:1。艾斯高賽後不敢邀功，他說：「皇馬擁有世界上最好的球員，實力非常強大，沒有團隊的合作今仗是不可能取勝。比賽初段我們不夠集中，以致先落後，之後球隊表現有所改善，我們要繼續保持目前的勢頭。為國家隊效力是所有球員的夢想，我希望可以在六、七年後重返國家隊，但先踢好貝迪斯的比賽。」皇馬輸波後與今晚才有比賽的巴塞隆拿同分但多打1場，並因對賽成績落後續居西甲次席。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
