        {
            "title": "倫敦新盤提供1及2房 售價約391萬起",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"倫敦新盤提供1及2房 售價約391萬起\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4747ee0f63865beb25a0d3a0cb0c71a2/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250228/_2025022809534784880.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">倫敦新盤提供1及2房 售價約391萬起</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>本港為英國新盤主要傾銷的地區之一，最新位於倫敦Wembley Park Gardens來港推售最新一期Stephenson House，售價約由英鎊39.9萬起，折合港幣約391萬。\n\n</p>\n<p>由英國著名發展商Barratt London發展的Wembley Park Gardens為全新地標性發展計劃，是次推售第2期首幢住宅大樓Stephenson House，項目坐落於溫布萊公園（Wembley Park）心臟地帶，樓高16層，提供111伙，設有1房及2房戶，面積由400至713方呎，現時售價由英鎊39.9萬起，折合港幣約391萬。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4108867/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"倫敦Wembley Park Gardens來港推售最新一期Stephenson House，售價約由港幣391萬起。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/195d0fdc23789af62fb5e5392dd6b5ad/2025-02/PRO10P04270225.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        倫敦Wembley Park Gardens來港推售最新一期Stephenson House，售價約由港幣391萬起。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>提供111伙</h2>\n<p>項目除禮賓服務外，貫穿各座平台花園，供住戶有充足的活動空間。Stephenson House首批住戶有望於2028年夏季入伙。\n\n</p>\n<p>Wembldy Park Gardens在交通上亦有一定優勢，毗鄰Wembley Park Tube Station，經兩條地鐵線Jubilee Line及Metropolitan Line，快捷前往倫敦市中心。\n\n</p><h2>面積400至713方呎</h2>\n<p>Wembley Park Gardens由5座高度不一的住宅大樓組成。所有單位均連接私人戶外空間，採用開放式布局。\n\n</p>\n<p>溫布萊區消閒活動應有盡有，無論是在The Troubadour欣賞舞台劇、在地標性的場館觀看體育比賽等，區內有各式各樣的餐廳和商戶，提供休閒娛樂體驗，住戶不乏好去處。發展商委託JLL仲量聯行協助銷售。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2055432/即時-地產-倫敦新盤提供1及2房-售價約391萬起",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-02 08:11:32",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "當代許褚｜170公斤男生8嚿腹肌 健身減肥意外「逆向」成力量舉冠軍",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/a218e66fa64e266c4fb7c4533a5f3440/2025-03/Clipboard41.png\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/50f1046ef67c71efa24636a5e8aa0102/1184aca8c2eb4d199a678ae0874d3fa7-f19b7e6d728875a80aed93b731fa3fe7-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67c39937081ea\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67c39937081ed\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"當代許褚｜170公斤男生8嚿腹肌 健身減肥意外「逆向」成力量舉冠軍\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/2057bb54c546aac3b8b2ea9f47f32b09/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030118375928292.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">當代許褚｜170公斤男生8嚿腹肌 健身減肥意外「逆向」成力量舉冠軍</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>在遼寧大連，一位體重340斤（170公斤）的00後男生因擁有八塊腹肌在網絡上走紅，被網友譽為當代許褚。該男生徐同學表示自己並沒有刻意扮許褚，只是因為喜歡盔甲道具，沒想到因此意外走紅。\n\n</p><h2>破亞州紀錄  目標世一</h2>\n<p>據了解，徐同學從17歲開始健身，已經堅持健身五六年，體重從最初的125公斤增長到現在的165至170公斤。他最初開始健身是為了減肥，但現在更多是為了參加比賽。他表示已經獲得了國際力量舉聯合會（International Powerlifting Federation），（簡稱IPF競技運動項目分深蹲、臥推、硬拉3項），力量舉青年組120公斤+亞州紀錄和深蹲紀錄，並希望將來能夠奪得一次世界冠軍。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"徐同學網上曬出的造型照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/450c098acc855b58ff2a1b51f7eb761c/2025-03/Clipboard38.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐同學網上曬出的造型照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"徐同學網上曬出的造型照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/067eb7428661cf4792f5b047fedf1437/2025-03/Clipboard39.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐同學網上曬出的造型照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"徐同學雖然170公斤但有8嚿腹肌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6922a7ca55413f38c36a5f498fa031f3/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-01-16h14m19s172.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐同學雖然170公斤但有8嚿腹肌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"徐同學喜愛盔甲道具。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/169ecc0eee92afddeee792c234cf7de3/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-01-16h14m22s832.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐同學喜愛盔甲道具。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"徐同學喜愛盔甲道具。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/912722cba567ac66272719cad14ec5f8/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-01-16h14m33s860.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐同學喜愛盔甲道具。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"徐同學去健身原為減肥結果體重增至170公斤左右。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2bdeda6697558fff81f7daae71cd803f/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-01-16h14m39s632.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐同學去健身原為減肥結果體重增至170公斤左右。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"徐同學去健身原為減肥結果體重增至170公斤左右。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b862a954c3cf68b74090e851bc0662cf/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-01-16h14m44s746.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐同學去健身原為減肥結果體重增至170公斤左右。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"徐同學穿盔甲，被稱為當代許褚。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/72558fc3f8449219de09ae9b0735c3f2/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-01-16h14m55s925.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐同學穿盔甲，被稱為當代許褚。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"徐同學堅持健身獲全國冠軍。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8f3eab2316dd17ab9f881a90da2c93ca/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-01-16h15m05s063.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐同學堅持健身獲全國冠軍。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"徐同學穿盔甲，被稱為當代許褚。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fd01486f5e4403113667db84c61164a0/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-01-16h15m13s197.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐同學穿盔甲，被稱為當代許褚。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"徐同學堅持健身獲全國冠軍。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b9f7e866bac5138130499c610f4c449f/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-01-16h15m17s158.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐同學堅持健身獲全國冠軍。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"徐同學堅持健身獲全國冠軍，目標是世界冠軍。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fd63aa731d46a2ac52d12c77df09a5ef/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-01-16h15m36s748.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐同學堅持健身獲全國冠軍，目標是世界冠軍。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/china-topics/3428139/%E6%B8%9B%E8%82%A5%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F42%E5%A4%A9%E7%98%A625%E5%85%AC%E6%96%A4-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A231%E6%AD%B2%E8%82%A5%E4%BB%94%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E9%80%86%E8%A5%B2%E6%88%904%E5%86%A0%E5%81%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%88%E7%94%9F\">減肥醫生｜42天瘦25公斤 武漢31歲「肥仔醫生」逆襲成4冠健美先生</a></strong>\n</p><h2>不會吃藥作弊</h2>\n<p>面對一些網友的質疑，徐同學解釋說，他參加的比賽都是國家性質的比賽，藥檢非常嚴格，不存在弄虛作假的情況。他還給網友們提供了健身建議，表示只要堅持自然也可以變得很好。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/world-topics/3428318/%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E9%A9%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%8C%91%E6%88%B0%E6%9C%88%E5%90%9E%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%83%E9%9A%BB%E8%9B%8B-%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%94%E5%91%88%E5%B7%A8%E8%AE%8A\">網紅驚人挑戰：月吞近千隻蛋 身體呈巨變</a></strong>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
