        {
            "title": "天文台｜本港今早有薄霧 日間部分時間有陽光及相當溫暖 最高氣溫約25度",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b94cc286234680a398e557fc7a2ad201/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250302/_2025030207023964483.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一股潮濕的海洋氣流正影響廣東沿岸。本港今早有薄霧，港內的能見度降至4000米左右。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日天氣預測，大致多雲。早晚潮濕有霧及有一兩陣微雨。日間部分時間有陽光及相當溫暖，最高氣溫約25度。吹輕微至和緩東南風。\n\n</p>\n<p>展望明日早晚仍然潮濕有霧，日間相當溫暖。星期二漸轉吹東北風及有驟雨。本週中至後期氣溫逐步下降及有幾陣雨，接近週末相當清涼，氣溫降至14度左右。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4112620/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"分區氣溫\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3b8ad3a3c121172618a35be957360f06/2025-03/2025-03-02_06_47_00.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        分區氣溫\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4112621/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"九天天氣預報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6c13ae95dd841b0c8b9552c15fe5ce75/2025-03/2025-03-02_06_47_27.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        九天天氣預報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4112622/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"最高氣溫約25度。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/18cd4d2dc94beacdc428ae8cff7be64d/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-02-06-34-18_004.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        最高氣溫約25度。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4112623/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本港今早有薄霧。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f33526c8e6eaa120de146b2ffe80eac7/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-02-06-34-13_002.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本港今早有薄霧。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4112624/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日間部分時間有陽光及相當溫暖。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d8735a56b7bfa413eb39b99997111c96/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-02-06-34-13_001.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間部分時間有陽光及相當溫暖。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>一股潮濕的海洋氣流會在今明兩日影響廣東沿岸，該區會出現回南天氣，早晚有霧，日間相當溫暖。預料一道冷鋒會在星期二橫過廣東，該區有驟雨及雷暴，天氣轉涼。受隨後的東北季候風及其補充影響，本週中至後期廣東沿岸氣溫逐步下降及有幾陣雨，接近週末天氣相當清涼。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
